<p><b><font color=#669900>SuSE YOU</font> - Install Updates over the Internet</b></p>
<p>New software can be easily installed or deleted without a trace in a centralized manner with <b>YaST2</b>.
<b>SuSE YOU (YaST Online Update)</b> makes sure your system is always up-to-date. At your request, <b>SuSE YOU</b> will connect
you to the SuSE Server and automatically install new patches and updates for your system.</p>
<p><b>New: SuSE YOU</b> can now be automatically controlled at the command line, quickly and efficiently.</p>